      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'The statues are back to how they where meant to be, and a ghost has been
    satisfied and opened the doors to the castle.


    Each room is haunted by a
    different ghost that has to be helped before they leave and let you have their
    relic.


    The first room to your right contains the relic cabinet, filling
    it up again with all the relics is your key to escape the front gates!'
